            "text": "<p><strong>Jon Sarkin</strong> (1953-2024) was a visionary outsider artist based in Gloucester, MA. Over the decades he created a massive body of work, spanning exhibitions, private sales, and museum placements.</p><p>His final workspace, Fish City Studios, is open to the public and remains a unique destination for visitors. That space, along with this site, are maintained by the official Sarkin Estate.</p><p>Collectors and curators can book concierge viewings both in person or virtually.</p>",
